ShapeOffset: Offset from the item location at which to test the overlap.  For example, you may need to offset vertically to avoid overlaps with flat ground.
OverlapChannel: geometry trace channel used for overlap
bOnlyBlockingHits: if set, overlap will look only for blocking hits
bOverlapComplex: if set, overlap will run on complex collisions
bSkipOverlapQuerier: if set, overlap will skip querier context hits
